name: 1969 Ford Mustang Mach 1
description:
One of Zenshy's favorite cars of all time, illustrated in a surreal Lo-fi setting with a cute lil sun that admires the car. The 1969 Ford Mustang elicits elegance like no other vehical. A beautiful car that is quite rare to this world and has only been seen by Zenshy THRICE.

PS: This is not Zenshy's depiction of what his future Mustang should look like.
PPS: This NFT holds a very rare Easter egg 👀
